platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The fabulous Bloons series has always been a colorful and clever spin on the tower-defense genre. When you’re up against human opponents in Bloons TD Battles, though, you’d better be as sharp as a blimp-bursting tack. Don’t be fooled by the mischievous monkeys—this is a game of riveting strategy and intense head-to-head hijinks.
